content: I think the app is great except for 2 things: often it shuts off after playing the tone once and also would like to have Bluetooth capability to pause or start the tone.

Have used this at the range on several occasions and I'm hitting the ball more consistently than ever. You still need to have a solid swing, but so far it's helping me hit it longer and straighter. And it is fun to use and play around with different swing speeds.
Excellent helps organise consistent rhythm right through the clubs
has helped with chipping and pitching the most

content: I had heard that the tempo is one of the most essential elements of a repeating golf swing. After purchasing "Mobile Golf Tempo", I really realized how true that is!  At first, I thought I would never swing that fast. I persevered, and now I have a more flowing golf swing, the ball goes straight and far. What impressed me the most was the tempo of the putting swing. I discovered that my downswing was really too slow. I now have a consistent tempo in the putting stroke that provides me a better distance control. I really recommend this app to golfers that want to improve their golf games.
